section.p:
FIRST Example 1a: List the first array of flights from
				Albuquerque to Atlanta after
				7pm.SELECT FIRST v FOR v IN schedule WHEN v.utc > "19:00" END AS evening_flights  
FROM `travel-sample`
WHERE type="route" AND airline="KL" AND sourceairport="ABQ" AND destinationairport="ATL"
AND ANY v IN schedule SATISFIES v.utc > "19:00" END;This
				results
				in:[
  {
    "evening_flights": [
      {
        "day": 1,
        "flight": "KL672",
        "utc": "19:19:00"
      }
    ]
  }
]
